13 thirty (30) years; and
14 2. The extension shall not include additional money awarded but
15 shall allow for payments to continue for the thirty-year period, or
16 until the net benefit for the new direct jobs for the original
17 contract has been fully paid out as calculated based upon the
18 original application.
