1 cale ndar quarter. The Tax Commission shall verify the actual gross
2 payroll for new direct jobs for the establishment for such calendar
3 quarter. If the Tax Commission is not able to provide such
4 verification utilizing all available resources, the Tax Commission
5 may request such additional information from the establishment as
6 may be necessary or may request the establishment to revise its
7 claim. An establishment may file for an extension of the initial
8 filing date with the Oklahoma Department of Commerce. Any such
9 extension shall be based solely upon an extraordinary adverse
